data.description: Immaculate Custom Ranch Home on Finished Basement in Sought After Golf/Swim/Tennis Community!  Great Room with Brick Fireplace and Built-Ins--Kitchen with Eat-In Area, Built-In Shelves, Built-In Microwave and Wall Oven, Gas Top Stove and Walk-In Pantry--Huge Master Suite with Sitting Area, Plantation Shutters, 2 Walk-In Closets with Access to Sunroom--Master Bath with 2 Vanities, Whirlpool Tub, and Oversized Tile Shower--Sitting Room with Wet Bar--Office/Den--Covered Porch with Wrap Around Deck and Hot Tub Overlooking Gorgeous Fenced Back Yard--Sunroom--Finished Basement has In-Law Suite Including Laundry Room (Laundry Chute), Bedroom, Full Bath, Rec Room, Utility Room, Workshop and Tons of Storage--Irrigation and Security Systems--Oversized 2-Car Garage.
